Package: hudson
Type: Package
Title: A mirrored Manhattan plot package
Version: 1.0.0
Author: person("Anastasia", "Lucas", email = "anastasia.lucas.bioinfo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <anastasia.lucas.bioinfo@gmail.com>
Description: This package creates mirrored Manhattan (Hudson) plots for *ome-wide association analyses, including, but not limited to, GWAS, PheWAS, and EWAS. 
License: GPL-3
Suggests: ggrepel
Depends: R (>= 3.2), ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0), gridExtra, grDevices, colorspace, ggiraph, cowplot 
